---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Automated Data Processing Platform">
  <Navbar />

  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">

    <p class="text-blue-400 mb-4">
      AWS • Jira • Lambda • S3 • CDK
    </p>

    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
      Automated Data Processing Platform
    </h1>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Problem</h2>

      <p class="text-slate-300">
        Operational teams were spending multiple days processing
        perception and transit-phase datasets. The process required
        significant manual intervention and engineering support,
        creating delays and reducing team efficiency.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Solution</h2>

      <p class="text-slate-300">
        Designed and implemented an event-driven automation platform
        integrating Jira workflows, AWS infrastructure, backend
        processing services, and automated validation systems.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Architecture</h2>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 bg-slate-900/40 font-mono text-slate-300">
        Jira Ticket<br/>
        ↓<br/>
        Webhook Trigger<br/>
        ↓<br/>
        Validation Service<br/>
        ↓<br/>
        Lambda Processing<br/>
        ↓<br/>
        S3 Storage<br/>
        ↓<br/>
        Status Monitoring<br/>
        ↓<br/>
        Jira Updates
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Responsibilities</h2>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-300 space-y-2">
        <li>Gathered requirements from stakeholders</li>
        <li>Designed system architecture</li>
        <li>Implemented backend services</li>
        <li>Provisioned AWS infrastructure using CDK</li>
        <li>Configured IAM, VPC, and storage resources</li>
        <li>Completed security review process</li>
        <li>Created documentation and operational runbooks</li>
        <li>Maintained production operations and monitoring</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Impact</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-4">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400">30 min</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Processing Time</div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-4">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400">7+</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Months in Production</div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-4">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400">10+</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Datasets Weekly</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>